author: tomdz
msg: Added first version of enhanced support for auto-incremented columns:
* a bean inserted via DynaSql will be updated with the real database-generated value (if the database supports something like 'select last_insert_id' or similar)
* ids in the data xml will be mapped transparently to the database-generated ones which makes it possible to define foreign key relationships in the xml file even for auto-increment pks
